ys. Remember that if you have any questions regarding topics covered in the course please feel free to ask. I\'m always happy to help!\n\nOver 300,000 people from around the world have enrolled in my courses\n\nMy courses are updated if needed\n\n\n\nPlease check out free lessons before buying! See for yourself the great quality of the course and enjoy it!\n\nBecome JavaScript Expert today!', '16659993453.jpg', 13.99, 0, 'javascript-from-beginner-to-expert-e5b239b8', 1, '2022-10-17 01:35:45', '2022-10-17 01:35:45'),
